Titolo: CSI: Miami (video game)

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: CSI: Miami is a video game based on the CSI: Miami television series. The game was developed by Radical Entertainment (under the 369 Interactive label), published by Ubisoft, and was released for the Microsoft Windows on April 24, 2004.  In 2008, Gameloft redeveloped the game for iOS.
This game, like CSI: Crime Scene Investigation, follows a distinct pattern of five cases, with the fifth case tying together the previous four.